{"tid":1741319,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟批評拘醫護違人權公約","createTime":"2019-11-20T09:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T10:03:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"456216d44047870afc6a949a437f241001c839ea","tid":1741319,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:34:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191120/6XYD35EUYUSHKQO6GFQSZJRV7Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191120%2F6XYD35EUYUSHKQO6GFQSZJRV7Q%2F&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLK0J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=5ffb19a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191120%2F6XYD35EUYUSHKQO6GFQSZJRV7Q%2F&h=4d5eed13\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191120/6XYD35EUYUSHKQO6GFQSZJRV7Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n歐盟批評拘醫護違人權公約<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191120/large/1574180283_ead8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191120%2Flarge%2F1574180283_ead8.jpg&h=3b64860a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歐盟外交和安全政策高級代表莫蓋里尼<br />\n<br />\n歐盟外交和安全政策高級代表莫蓋里尼（Federica Mogherini）前天為本港警民暴力衝突升級發聲明，呼籲香港各方必須克制，積極緩和局勢，強調任何暴力都不能接受，又指執法當局的行動必須合乎比例。<br />\n<br />\n莫蓋里尼表示，只有包容性和真誠對話、和解與社區參與等建立互信的措施，才會有可持續的解決方法；對於示威潮的暴力、武力使用和根本原因的全面調查，是令局勢降溫的關鍵。她又指，香港的高度自治必須按《基本法》和國際承諾保留，持續尊重基本權利和自由及司法獨立，仍是香港發展的基要所在。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聯合國：理大內人道狀況惡化<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：手足：想食pizza可能係最後一餐<br />\n<br />\n歐盟對外事務部發言人科齊揚契奇在類似呼籲之餘，指從理大衝突的新聞報道看到現場急救者及其他醫護人員試圖協助傷者時被執法人員拘留，指「這種現象令人極度關注」，類似行為如發生在戰爭時期，已違反國際人道法《日內瓦公約》。<br />\n<br />\n另外，德國聯邦政府發言人德默爾前天表示，德國高度關注香港局勢，呼籲香港警察和示威者克制並表現出對話的意願，期待盡快實施緩和情勢的具體措施，讓爭端和平解決。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處發表聲明，指理工大學內被困者的人道狀況「明顯惡化」，促香港當局盡一切辦法，緩和在理工大學的局勢。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/中央社"},{"pid":"b6b46431594deba561107a74000c7163eeb92173","tid":1741319,"uid":70227,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:37:28.000Z","msg":"歐盟終於出聲<br />\n不過同聯合國一樣得把口多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baea014918425370c92fcd30d18b4d8ed98fcdcc","tid":1741319,"uid":65074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:37:40.000Z","msg":"歐盟終於訓醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbbf76cefba7ca43c5df7cb28d9105b8ea19f7a3","tid":1741319,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:38:12.000Z","msg":"做嘢未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57dfdc7b0b2deb2704c02a9cd8596c1c9f7a5982","tid":1741319,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:38:40.000Z","msg":"then"},{"pid":"d849c6c3cd761e3e4a6dbe3f7dd3e88f4ed58281","tid":1741319,"uid":257131,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b6b46431594deba561107a74000c7163eeb92173","tid":1741319,"uid":70227,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:37:28.000Z","msg":"歐盟終於出聲<br />\n不過同聯合國一樣得把口多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:39:07.000Z","msg":"算啦，肯出聲已經好好，佢地都冇乜野可以做到"},{"pid":"589dd61a9289aee8b65c7e6fd6b76bf203af916c","tid":1741319,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c340b45ba0855fe36dbf6cca06012de71e22ead1","tid":1741319,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d849c6c3cd761e3e4a6dbe3f7dd3e88f4ed58281","tid":1741319,"uid":257131,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b6b46431594deba561107a74000c7163eeb92173","tid":1741319,"uid":70227,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:37:28.000Z","msg":"歐